WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.940 --> 00:00:06.080
You took such a strong drug, I don't believe you can still control it.

2
00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:08.720
Tonight I will break the bones of you sick man,

3
00:00:09.040 --> 00:00:10.280
I have to capture you too.

4
00:00:13.630 --> 00:00:16.160
Why is it you again? You haven’t left yet?

5
00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:18.610
Brother, I was wrong.

6
00:00:19.270 --> 00:00:22.490
It’s Yaoyao’s fault tonight. Don't be angry with Yaoyao.

7
00:00:22.710 --> 00:00:23.570
Forgive Yaoyao.

8
00:00:24.300 --> 00:00:25.980
How could I be angry with someone like you?

9
00:00:26.760 --> 00:00:29.140
Brother, I've already packed my things.

10
00:00:29.810 --> 00:00:31.390
We'll leave at first light tomorrow.

11
00:00:32.040 --> 00:00:37.090
I was wrong this time, so I came here to apologize to you.

12
00:00:38.260 --> 00:00:39.970
No. Noodle brother

13
00:00:39.970 --> 00:00:41.810
If you don't drink this cup of tea

14
00:00:41.810 --> 00:00:43.550
I’m still angry with Yaoyao

15
00:00:43.550 --> 00:00:52.870
What is Bian doing?

16
00:01:04.120 --> 00:01:06.680
I won't leave unless I stay here.

17
00:01:09.220 --> 00:01:09.440
I'm tired of playing here.

